>I'm using the morph3D demo from the Aminet.

Morph3D is a demo compiled with StormMesa 2, which is very old and
doesn't provide any hardware acceleration. You need to download the
demos which you can found in the download section of the 3DWorld
web pages. Those demos also are very small compared to the old
ones, because StormMesa 3 has become a shared library in contrary
to its predecessor, which was only provided as link library and
therefore is compiled into every single demo, no matter how simple
it is.

